review_content: Alice is a very patient and knowledgeable tutor. My child learned a lot in just a few sessions.
Bob did a good job teaching my child, though there were some challenges in communication.
Charlie was okay, but my child had some difficulties following the lessons.
Diana has been a fantastic tutor. She’s made learning fun and engaging for my child.
Edward did not meet my expectations. I felt the sessions were not very helpful.
Fiona is a solid tutor, but I believe she can improve on the pace of the lessons.
George is an exceptional tutor! He really knows how to explain complex topics in a simple way.
Hannah was good, but there’s room for improvement in keeping my child focused.
Ian’s lessons were very informative, but I think my child would benefit from more hands-on activities.
Jenna is a wonderful tutor. My child is always excited for the lessons.
